summary: 该插件用于检测目标系统是否存在Apache Struts2 (s2-033) CVE-2016-3087远程代码执行漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the target system has the Apache Struts2 (s2-033) CVE-2016-3087 RCE vulnerability by sending a specific payload to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
